sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant UI as MissionCommand page
  participant API as GET /api/mission-command/bootstrap
  participant Handler as handleMissionCommandBootstrapGet
  participant DB as SQLite

  User->>UI: Open /missionCommand
  UI->>API: GET /api/mission-command/bootstrap
  API->>Handler: withDb(load projection + operator + doctrine + source maps)
  Handler->>DB: SELECT runtime projection datasets

  alt query/db failure
    DB-->>Handler: error
    Handler-->>API: throw
    API-->>UI: 500 {error,traceId}
    UI-->>User: mission bootstrap error state
  else success
    DB-->>Handler: rows
    Handler-->>API: 200 bootstrap payload
    API-->>UI: JSON payload
    UI-->>User: render mission hierarchy + warnings
  end
